 of creation thereof with A Rated Banks and (v) mutual funds that invest solely in one or more of the investments described in clauses (i) through (iv) above; (d) investments in other Borrowers; (e) other investments not to exceed $1,000,000 in the aggregate; (f) investments in foreign Subsidiaries (other than Permitted Breaker Technology Ltd. Intercompany Loans and Advances) not to exceed $500,000 in the aggregate (for the purposes of this clause (f), assets of a Credit Party which are used by a foreign Subsidiary or located on the premises of a foreign Subsidiary shall be treated as an investment in such foreign Subsidiary), and (g) investments consisting of Permitted Breaker Technology Ltd. Intercompany Loans and Advances.
