Borrower shall not breach or fail to comply with any of the following financial covenants, each of which shall be calculated in accordance with GAAP consistently applied:
(a) . Astec and its Subsidiaries shall have on a consolidated basis (i) at the end of each Fiscal Quarter (other than the Fiscal Quarter ending on June 30, 2003), a Consolidated Fixed Charge Coverage Ratio for the 12-month period then ended of not less than 1.25 to 1.00 and (ii) at the end of the Fiscal Quarter ending on June 30, 2003, a Consolidated Fixed Charge Coverage Ratio for the 12-month period then ended of not less than 1.00 to 1.00.
Minimum Consolidated Fixed Charge Coverage Ratio
