Item 1.01 Entry into a Material Definitive Agreement.
On December 22, 2005, Astec Industries, Inc. (the "Company") entered into an Amended and Restated Shareholder Protection Rights Agreement pursuant to which Mellon Investor Services LLC will serve as Rights Agent (the "Amended and Restated Rights Agreement"). The Amended and Restated Rights Agreement, among other things, extends the expiration date of the Rights Agreement from December 22, 2005 to December 22, 2015 and changes the purchase price from $36.00 to $72.00.
The foregoing description of the Amended and Restated Rights Agreement is a general description only and is qualified in its entirety by reference to Exhibit 4.1 hereto, the contents of which are incorporated by reference herein.
