Item 8.01. Other Events.
     On July 31, 2007, Astec Industries issued a press release announcing the consummation of its acquisition of Peterson, Inc.  A copy of this press release is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K and is incorporated herein by reference.
 
 
