Item 8.01. Other Events.
     On October 5, 2011 Astec Industries issued a press release announcing the consummation of its acquisition of the GEFCO and STECO divisions of Blue Tee Corp.  A copy of this press release is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K and is incorporated herein by reference.
 
